ast.source:
You have enabled OTEL export via the `OTEL_ENABLED` or `LANGSMITH_OTEL_ENABLED` environment variable, but have not initialized the required OTEL instances. Please add:
```
import { initializeOTEL } from "langsmith/experimental/otel/setup";
initializeOTEL();
```
at the beginning of your code.

ast.target:
您已通过 `OTEL_ENABLED` 或 `LANGSMITH_OTEL_ENABLED` 环境变量启用了 OTEL 导出，但尚未初始化所需的 OTEL 实例。请在代码开头添加：
```
import { initializeOTEL } from "langsmith/experimental/otel/setup";
initializeOTEL();
```
